{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"pi01","text":"This area of my website is intended to act somewhat like a blog. But none of these are really blog posts or articles. They are more like a collection of posts and experiments. Here you will find no seriousness, no professional tone, and no strict rules, just my own personal take on things.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}
